column5: Hi all, Holiday off to a good start, been out twice, finally landed a tarpon the first day, and lost a humungous snook too. Got a bunch of eater fish that day too. This morning I lost something huge and then managed to land this guy.
That'll feed the family for a bit Simon!!!!! HH
Wow! That's awesome Simon! Have fun on the Vaca!
Nice snapper there LA not sure one guy should say that to another! Any way where abouts are you and what resort are you staying at? Bill
Nice fish and a warm place what could be better when it is snowing at home. Art
